item.title: Advent of Code 2024 - C#
item.description: Advent of Code 2024. Eric Wastl. adventofcode.com . Accessed Jun 25, 2025. Objective: Get better at C#. Why doesn’t dchege711/blog@3483b54 add hyperlinks in .cs code comments? My MacBook Pro (Retina, 15-inch, Mid 2015) can only update to Monterey 12. Ventura 13 and newer don’t support my Mac. It seems Mac moves pretty fast; Tahoe 26 oldest supported Mac is MacBook Pro (16-inch, 2019).
